issue.title: Have convenience functions for easily analyzing your code and creating a container
Allow Inject values to be derived from an arbitrary store
Allow Container to make arbitrary objects with autowired parameters
Allow Container to be generated by multiple backing libraries
Add API for creating a type-safe configuration to be consumed by Services
Allow a type to be marked as a service that should be re-instantiated on each call
Support injecting scalar values based on active profile
Provide API for easily configuring third-party code that can't be annotated
Allow retrieving a collection of Services matching a given type
Allow service to have custom name instead of forcing FCQN
Mark Service as Primary to resolve multiple aliases

Feature/profiles as argument (#30)

* Remove ServiceProfile attribute, move profiles to Service argument

* Move profiles to annotation arguments, retrieve value at runtime

* Implement ContainerFactoryOptionsBuilder

* Fix profile serialization/deserialization

* Better handle named/unnamed annotation arguments

* make inject service provide an AnnotationValue

* make inject service provide an AnnotationValue

* move class shouldn't be in public api to anon class

* Update to use correct dummy apps

* update changelog

* Update docs, remove references to ServiceProfile
